'''Awa Traoré''' , ni umukinnyi wa firime wo muri [[Mali]]  .  Usibye gutanga icyerekezo, Traoré ni umuyobozi wungirije, uwahimba ndetse n'umwanditsiwa filimi.

== Umwuga ==
Traoré yatangiye umwuga we muri film ya ''L'enfant noir'' 1995. Nyuma yaje kuba 'umuhigi' muri filime ngufi ya ''Denko yo'' mu 1993 iyobowe na Mohamed Camara . Iyi filime yakiriwe neza kandi yegukana Grand Prix mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya sinema mpuzamahanga rya Clermont-Ferrand,  igihembo cya filime ngufi nziza mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Friborg ndetse n’igihembo cya Golden Danzante mu iserukiramuco rya Filime rya Huesca. 

